0an%20area%20of%2070%2C000%20square%20meters%20(more%20than%20750%2C000%20square%20feet)%2C%20with%2050%2C000%20square%20meters%20(around%20540%2C000%20square%20feet)%20of%20the%20Wildberries%20warehouse%20collapsing%2C%20according%20to%20Russia's%20Emergency%20Situations%20Ministry.%20No%20casualties%20were%20reported.%20Russia's%20Emergency%20Situations%20Ministry%20said%20that%20firefighters%20had%20been%20able%20to%20prevent%20the%20fire%20from%20spreading%20across%20the%20entire%20area%20of%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8Bthe%20warehouse%20complex%20and%20to%20an%20electrical%20substation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fhuge-fire-engulfs-warehouse-in-russia-outside-the-city-of-st-petersburg%2Farticleshow%2F106821168.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fhuge-fire-engulfs-warehouse-in-russia-outside-the-city-of-st-petersburg%2Famp_articleshow%2F106821168.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fhuge-fire-engulfs-warehouse-in-russia-outside-the-city-of-st-petersburg%2Famp_articleshow%2F106821168.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Yatra%20To%20Start%20From%20Manipur's%20Thoubal%20Today%20Amid%20Ethnic%20Tensions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECongress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20flanked%20by%20party%20leaders%20Okram%20Ibobi%20Singh%2C%20Keisham%20Meghachandra%20Singh%2C%20Nabam%20Tuki%2C%20and%20Gaikhangam%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20that%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20before%20the%20country%20polarisation%2C%20economic%20inequalities%2C%20and%20political%20authoritarianism.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20yatra%20will%20be%20flagged%20off%20from%20a%20private%20ground%20in%20Thoubal%20district%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20the%20party's%20initial%20choice.%20The%20BJP-led%20state%20government%20had%20given%20the%20Congress%20conditional%20approval%20to%20flag%20off%20the%20yatra%20from%20Imphal%2C%20restricting%20the%20number%20of%20participants.%20The%20Congress%20chose%20the%20other%20option.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Thoubal%20district%20administration%20has%20also%20imposed%20some%20restrictions%20on%20the%20event%20such%20as%20the%20duration%20should%20not%20exceed%20an%20hour%20and%20the%20number%20of%20participants%20should%20not%20cross%203%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20yatra%20will%20be%20in%20Manipur%20for%20a%20day%20and%20cover%20a%20little%20over%20100%20km.%20Ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20past%20nine%20months%20have%20killed%20over%20180%20and%20internally%20displaced%20thousands.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBefore%20starting%20the%20yatra%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20pay%20homage%20to%20martyrs%20at%20the%20Khongjom%20War%20Memorial%20in%20Thoubal%2C%20built%20in%20memory%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20last%20Anglo-Manipur%20War%20in%201891.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20influential%20civil%20society%20group%20People's%20Alliance%20for%20Peace%20and%20Progress%20Manipur%20(PAPPM)%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday%20alleged%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20yatra%20%26quot%3Bis%20in%20support%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%26quot%3B%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%20ethnic%20tensions%20in%20Manipur%20where%20the%20issue%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20coming%20from%20Myanmar%20is%20extremely%20sensitive%20and%20controversial.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BRegrettably%2C%20we%20must%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20rehabilitation%20efforts%20for%20Kuki%20refugees%20in%20Manipur%2C%20inclusive%20of%20granting%20voting%20rights%2C%20were%20initiated%20by%20successive%20Congress-led%20central%20governments.%20The%20primary%20motive%20behind%20these%20endeavours%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20strategic%20objective%20of%20consolidating%20political%20support%20by%20integrating%20the%20refugees%20(illegal%20immigrants)%2C%20into%20a%20potential%20voter%20base%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20PAPPM%20chief%20M%20Bobby%20Meetei%20said%20in%20the%20statement%C2%A0on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20highlight%20that%20the%20present%20violent%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%20is%20the%20result%20of%20uncontrolled%20influx%20of%20Kuki%20refugees%20(illegal%20immigrants)%20to%20Manipur%20especially%20from%20Myanmar%20(previously%20Burma)%20and%20their%20rehabilitation%20in%20Manipur%20with%20voting%20rights%20after%20merger%20to%20the%20Indian%20Union%20in%201949%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PAPPM%20alleged%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Kuki%20tribes%20claim%20the%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20only%20wants%20to%20grab%20land%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20so%20invented%20excuses%20to%20engineer%20fear%20among%20the%20Meities%20against%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%2C%20eventually%20leading%20to%20the%20violence.%20Following%20the%20outbreak%20of%20clashes%20on%20May%203%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Meiteis%2C%20however%2C%20maintain%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20always%20been%20working%20towards%20demanding%20a%20separate%20land%20and%20their%20protest%20against%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20category%20was%20only%20an%20excuse%20to%20bring%20a%20crisis%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705172280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0bh2q7j8_congress-imphal_625x300_14_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongresss-yatra-to-start-today-from-manipur-scarred-with-ethnic-illegal-immigrant-tensions-4857915%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress's%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20led%20by%20