l%3E%3Cli%3EOhio%20authorities%20have%20accused%20a%20woman%20of%20faking%20her%20daughter's%20cancer%20diagnosis%20to%20raise%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20local%20organization%20donated%20%248%2C000%20to%20the%20child's%20purported%20medical%20expenses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPamela%20Reed%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20theft%20by%20deception%2C%20a%20fourth-degree%20felony%2C%20the%20sheriff's%20department%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20in%20Ohio%20say%20a%20woman%20faked%20her%20daughter's%20cancer%20diagnosis%20and%20used%20it%20to%20raise%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20online%20fundraisers%20for%20her%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Noble%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D681626940812388%26id%3D100068952648446%26mibextid%3D9R9pXO%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20Wednesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20deputies%20arrested%20Pamela%20Reed%2C%2041%2C%20on%20January%204%20and%20charged%20her%20with%20theft%20by%20deception%2C%20a%20fourth-degree%20felony.%20A%20judge%20set%20Reed's%20bond%20at%20%2450%2C000%2C%20authorities%20said%20in%20their%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheriff's%20office%20said%20it%20received%20a%20tip%20that%20a%20local%20child%20was%20being%20used%20to%20improperly%20raise%20money%20based%20on%20the%20public%20portrayal%20that%20they%20had%20cancer.%20Several%20local%20organizations%20donated%20money%20to%20the%20child%2C%20including%20one%20that%20made%20a%20donation%20of%20%248%2C000%2C%20the%20sheriff's%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24356846-preed-affidavit-of-facts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprobable%20cause%20affidavit%3C%2Fa%3E%20obtained%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flawandcrime.com%2Fcrime%2Fmother-who-allegedly-faked-daughters-cancer-for-cash-grab-arrested%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELaw%20%26amp%3B%2