et%20Child%20In%20Bengaluru%2C%20Then%20Checked%20Into%20Goa%20Hotel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20allegedly%20denying%20him%20a%20chance%20to%20meet%20his%20son%20for%20at%20least%20three%20weeks%20despite%20a%20court%20order%2C%20the%20CEO%20accused%20of%20murdering%20the%20four-year-old%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20child%20in%20a%20Bengaluru%20locality%20on%20January%207%2C%20a%20day%20after%20she%20had%20already%20checked%20into%20a%20serviced%20apartment%20in%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20of%20Suchana%20Seth's%20husband%2C%20Venkat%20Raman%2C%20said%20the%20CEO%20sent%20an%20e-mail%20to%20Mr%20Raman%20on%20January%206%20and%20said%20he%20could%20meet%20their%20child%20the%20next%20day.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengaluru-ceo-suchana-seths-estranged-husband-in-sons-murder-case-4854793%5C%22%3Epolice%20complaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20lodged%20by%20the%20manager%20of%20a%20Goa%20serviced%20apartment%2C%20however%2C%20she%20had%20checked%20in%20with%20their%20four-year-old%20son%20on%20the%20very%20night%20this%20e-mail%20was%20sent.%20The%20room%20had%20been%20booked%2C%20and%20paid%20for%2C%20until%20January%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raman's%20lawyer%20said%20the%20husband%20was%20not%20aware%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20child%20were%20in%20Goa%20and%20he%20went%20to%20the%20designated%20meeting%20spot%2C%20waited%20for%20an%20hour%2C%20sent%20her%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20and%20two%20e-mails%20asking%20if%20everything%20was%20okay%2C%20and%20then%20left%20when%20she%20did%20not%20turn%20up.%20The%20four-year-old's%20body%20was%20discovered%20in%20Seth's%20suitcase%20on%20January%208%2C%20when%20she%20had%20left%20Goa%20and%20was%20headed%20to%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengaluru-ceo-suchana-seths-estranged-husband-in-sons-murder-case-4854793%5C%22%3Erecorded%20his%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20Goa%20police%20on%20Saturday%20afternoon%20and%20said%20he%20had%20not%20been%20allowed%20to%20meet%20the%20child%20for%20the%20past%20five%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Seeking%20Retribution%20Futile'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Hindi%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Mr%20Raman's%20lawyer%2C%20Azhar%20Meer%2C%20said%20seeking%20retribution%20after%20the%20child's%20death%20was%20futile%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20expect%20any%20justice.%20The%20child%20is%20dead%20and%20why%20the%20mother%20did%20it%20is%20immaterial%2C%20in%20a%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20the%20trigger%20for%20the%20murder%20could%20be%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20only%20guess.%20A%20mother%20doing%20this%20to%20her%20child%20is%20so%20unnatural%20that%20no%20answer%20can%20give%20anyone%20any%20closure.%20As%20for%20the%20trigger%2C%20we%20can%20guess%20that%20she%20probably%20did%20not%20want%20the%20son%20to%20meet%20the%20father%20and%20had%2C%20thus%2C%20filed%20cases.%20(In%20a%20custody%20dispute)%20every%20party%20thinks%20they%20have%20a%20right%2C%20but%20the%20child%20has%20an%20equal%20right%20to%20receive%20love%20from%20both%20the%20mother%20and%20the%20father.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Meer%20said%20that%20the%20Bengaluru%20family%20court%2C%20where%20the%20custody%20case%20was%20being%20heard%2C%20had%20ruled%20progressively%20in%20Mr%20Raman's%20favour%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20He%20said%20Mr%20Raman%20was%20initially%20allowed%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20child%20on%20the%20phone%20or%20over%20video%20call%2C%20and%20then%20permitted%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20him%20within%20the%20court%20premises%20once%20in%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said%2C%20the%20husband%20was%20allowed%20to%20meet%20the%20child%20at%20home%20from%20morning%20to%20evening.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20probably%20angry%20that%20the%20judge%20had%20been%20ruling%20in%20the%20father's%20favour%2C%20but%20why%20kill%20the%20child%20because%20of%20this%20anger%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Seth's%20claims%20that%20Mr%20Raman%20was%20harassing%20her%2C%20Mr%20Meer%20said%20that%20was%20a%20lie.%20%26quot%3BBut%20even%20if%20we%20assume%20that%20it%20was%20true%2C%20what%20was%20the%20child's%20fault%3F%20The%20child%20wasn't%20harassing%20her.%20She%20could%20have%20taken%20out%20her%20anger%20at%20the%20husband%2C%20why%20take%20it%20out%20on%20the%20child...%20There%20is%20someone%20in%20custody%20in%20whose%20bag%20the%20child%20was%20found%20and%20then%20there's%20the%20husband%20who%20had%20to%20conduct%20his%20last%20rites.%20You%20can't%20imagine%20what%20he%20is%20going%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Refused%20To%20Comply'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20said%20the%20last%20court%20order%2C%20on%20November%2020%2C%20permitted%20Mr%20Raman%20to%20meet%20his%20son%20once%20every%20week%2C%20from%20morning%20to%20evening.%20The%20meetings%20would%20take%20place%20on%20Sunday%20and%20the%20last%20one%20was%20on%20December%2010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20didn't%20send%20the%20boy%20for%20three%20or%20four%20weeks.%20There%20were%20multiple%20requests%2C%20but%20she%20refused%20to%20comply.%20January%207%2C%20Sunday%2C%20is%20when%20the%20child%20was%20taken%20from%20this%20world%20and%20we%20had%20hoped%20that%20Mr%20Raman%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20meet%20him%20that%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Mr%20Raman%20knew%20that%20Seth%20and%20the%20child%20were%20in%20Goa%2C%20Mr%20Meer%20asserted%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20he%20absolutely%20did%20not.%20On%20January%206%2C%20she%20had%20written%20an%20e-mail%20asking%20Mr%20Raman%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20child%20on%C2%A0%20the%20morning%20of%20January%207%20from%20Sadashiva%20Nagar%20in%20Bengaluru.%20He%20went%20there%20and%20waited%20from%2010%20am%20to%2011%20am%2C%20went%20back%20home%20and%20then%20left%20for%20some%20work%20in%20the%20evening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20leaving%20the%20meeting%20spot%2C%20he%20sent%20her%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20saying%20'I%20am%20here'%20and%20also%20sent%20two%20e-mails%20saying%20he%20was%20waiting%20and%20that%20he%20hoped%20everything%20was%20okay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20said%20Suchana%20had%20requested%20that%20the%20pick-up%20and%20drop-off%20point%20for%20Mr%20Raman's%20meetings%20with%20his%20son%20be%20a%20public%20place.%20%26quot%3BIn%20her%20words%2C%20it%20was%20a%20child-safe%20place%20or%20something%20like%20that%2C%20and%20she%20used%20to%20use%20a%20coffee%20shop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Suchana%20Seth%20had%20tried%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%20after%20allegedly%20murdering%20her%20son.%20She%20was%20caught%20in%20Karnataka's%20Chitradurga%20on%20January%208%20-%20when%20she%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20with%20the%20child's%20body%20in%20a%20suitcase%20-%20after%20the%20staff%20at%20the%20service%20apartment%20alerted%20the%20police%20about%20bloodstains%20being%20found%20in%20her%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705165140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkr8q1bso_suchana-seth_625x300_09_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fceo-asked-husband-to-meet-child-in-bengaluru-then-checked-into-goa-hotel-4857369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20allegedly%20denying%20him%20a%20chance%20to%20meet%20his%20son%20for%20at%20least%203%20weeks%2C%20the%20CEO%20accused%20of%20murdering%20the%20four-year-old%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20child%20in%20a%20Bengaluru%20locality%20on%20January%207%2C%20a%20day%20after%20she%20had%20already%20checked%20into%20a%20Goa%20hotel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2