t%2Ffull-house-at-ira-khan-nupur-shikhares-wedding-reception-see-fam-jam-pics-4856980%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ffull-house-at-ira-khan-nupur-shikhares-wedding-reception-see-fam-jam-pics-4856980%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Aren't%20In%20Anyone's%20Backyard%26quot%3B%3A%20Maldives%20President%20Amid%20Row%20With%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReturning%20home%20after%20a%20five-day%20high-profile%20state%20visit%20to%20China%2C%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20on%20Saturday%20struck%20a%20defiant%20note%20saying%20that%20his%20country%20may%20be%20small%20but%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20give%20them%20the%20license%20to%20bully%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20came%20amid%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaldives-india-news-easemytrip-maldives-tourism-bodys-plea-to-easemytrip-indian-brothers-sisters-4833882%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediplomatic%20row%20with%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20derogatory%20social%20media%20posts%20by%20three%20of%20his%20ministers%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20be%20small%20but%20this%20doesn't%20give%20them%20the%20license%20to%20bully%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Muizzu%2C%20who%20is%20regarded%20as%20a%20pro-China%20leader%2C%20said%20without%20naming%20any%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20we%20have%20small%20islands%20in%20this%20ocean%2C%20we%20have%20a%20vast%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%20of%20900%2C000%20square%20km.%20Maldives%20is%20one%20of%20the%20countries%20with%20the%20biggest%20share%20of%20this%20ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media%20on%20his%20arrival%20from%20China%20after%20concluding%20the%20state%20visit%2C%20the%20first%20after%20assuming%20office%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20ocean%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20a%20specific%20country.%20This%20(Indian)%20Ocean%20also%20belongs%20to%20all%20countries%20situated%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20in%20an%20apparent%20jibe%20at%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20aren't%20in%20anyone's%20backyard.%20We%20are%20an%20independent%20and%20sovereign%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20Maldives%20Sun%20Online%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%20to%20China%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmaldives-lakshadweep-row-president-urges-china-to-send-more-tourists-amid-row-india-pm-modi-with-india-4830115%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMuizzu%20held%20talks%20with%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20which%20the%20two%20countries%20signed%2020%20agreements.%20%26quot%3BThe%20two%20sides%20agree%20to%20continue%20firmly%20supporting%20each%20other%20in%20safeguarding%20their%20respective%20core%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20joint%20statement%20issued%20at%20the%20end%20of%20Muizzu's%20talks%20with%20the%20top%20Chinese%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20firmly%20supports%20the%20Maldives%20in%20upholding%20its%20national%20sovereignty%2C%20independence%20and%20national%20dignity%2C%20respects%20and%20supports%20the%20Maldives'%20exploration%20of%20a%20development%20path%20that%20suits%20its%20national%20conditions%2C%20and%20firmly%20opposes%20external%20interference%20in%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20the%20Maldives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20without%20referring%20to%20any%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20media%20briefing%20in%20Male%2C%20Muizzu%20said%20China%20has%20granted%20USD%20130%20million%20in%20assistance%20for%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20said%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20USD%20130%20million%20assistance%20will%20be%20spent%20on%20redeveloping%20the%20roads%20in%20Male%2C%20where%20the%20mayor%20election%20is%20being%20held%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20former%20Mayor%20of%20the%20capital%20city%20before%20getting%20elected%20to%20the%20Presidency%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20approximately%20USD%20130%20million%20in%20grants.%20This%20will%20be%20spent%20on%20developmental%20projects.%20The%20biggest%20spending%20will%20be%20on%20the%20development%20of%20the%20roads%20of%20Male%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20local%20news%20portal%20Sun%20Online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20China's%20Ambassador%20to%20Maldives%20Wang%20Lixin%20said%20Maldives%20will%20receive%20support%20for%20more%20development%20projects%20from%20Beijing%20if%20they%20align%20with%20President%20Xi's%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%2C%20who%20accompanied%20Muizzu%20on%20his%20visit%20to%20China%2C%20said%20there%20are%20three%20key%20factors%20to%20the%20strong%20relations%20between%20Maldives%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20and%20most%20important%20factor%20is%20mutual%20political%20trust.%20The%20second%20factor%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20docking%20of%20President%20Xi's%20initiatives%20and%20the%20national%20development%20strategy%20of%20President%20Muizzu.%20And%20with%20this%20docking%2C%20I%20think%20we%20can%20decide%20on%20more%20projects%20that%20benefit%20the%20Maldivian%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%20said%20that%20the%20third%20one%20is%20to%20follow%20the%20principle%20of%20extensive%20consultation%2C%20joint%20construction%2C%20and%20also%20shared%20benefits.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20with%20these%20three%20key%20factors%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20very%20fruitful%20and%20sustainable%20cooperation%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20this%20visit%2C%20the%20two%20heads%20of%20state%20have%20announced%20the%20elevation%20of%20our%20bilateral%20relations%20to%20a%20Comprehensive%20Strategic%20Cooperative%20Partnership.%20This%20will%20provide%20a%20strong%20political%20guarantee%20for%20the%20future%20cooperation%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Sun%20Online%20said%2C%20quoting%20her%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu's%20visit%20to%20China%20was%20marred%20by%20the%20diplomatic%20row%20with%20India%20over%20derogatory%20remarks%20by%20his%20ministers%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20the%20release%20of%20a%20report%20by%20the%20EU%20Election%20Observation%20Mission%20of%20Maldives%20that%20said%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20of%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20(PPM)%20and%20the%20People's%20National%20Congress%20(PNC)%20deployed%20anti-India%20sentiments%20and%20attempted%20to%20spread%20disinformation%20in%20the%202023%20presidential%20elections%20in%20which%20Muizzu%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EU%20report%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20Muizzu's%20Presidential%20election%20last%20November%20as%20he%20contested%20as%20part%20of%20PPM%20headed%20at%20that%20time%20by%20former%20pro-China%20President%20Abdullah%20Yameen%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20serving%20a%20prison%20sentence%20for%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Muizzu's%20visit%20to%20Beijing%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20signed%20a%20USD%2050%20million%20agreement%20to%20develop%20an%20integrated%20tourism%20zone%20in%20Hulhumale'%20besides%20building%2030%2C000%20social%20housing%20units%20in%20Rasmale'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20will%20also%20provide%20grant%20assistance%20for%20the%20development%20of%20a%20100-bed%20tertiary%20hospital%20in%20Vilimale'%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India-built%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Memorial%20Hospital%20(IGMH)%20in%20Male%20is%20regarded%20as%20the%20biggest%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20300-bed%20hospital%20was%20built%20in%201992%20by%20India%20well%20before%20China%20made%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20island%20nation%20with%20infrastructure%20projects.%20The%20IGMH%20was%20remodified%20with%20Indian%20assistance%20in%202018%20with%20the%20additio