-aamir-khan-reena-dutta-kiran-rao-to-miss-the-function-heres-why-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F106818186.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Army%20Launches%20Operation%20To%20Thwart%20Pak's%20Plan%20To%20Revive%20Terrorism%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20step%20towards%20thwarting%20Pakistan's%20attempts%20to%20increase%20terrorist%20activities%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20is%20launching%20Operation%20Sarvashakti%2C%20where%20the%20security%20forces%20will%20be%20targeting%20the%20terrorists%20operating%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20mountain%20ranges%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20Pakistani%20proxy%20terrorist%20groups%20have%20tried%20to%20revive%20terrorism%20in%20the%20South%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20ranges%20especially%20in%20the%20Rajouri%20Poonch%20sector%2C%20where%20around%2020%20troops%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20attacks%20by%20terrorists%2C%20with%20the%20latest%20being%20on%20December%2021%2C%20when%20four%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20in%20the%20Dera%20ki%20Gali%20area%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOperation%20Sarvashakti%20would%20be%20to%20carry%20out%20combined%20counter-terrorist%20operations%20from%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20ranges%20where%20the%20formations%20of%20the%20Srinagar-based%20Chinar%20Corps%20along%20with%20the%20Nagrota-headquartered%20White%20Knight%20Corps%20would%20be%20carrying%20out%20simultaneous%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20in%20the%20security%20forces%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%2C%20CRPF%2C%20Special%20Operations%20Group%2C%20and%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%20would%20be%20working%20in%20close%20coordination%20to%20thwart%20Pakistani%20designs%20to%20revive%20terrorist%20activities%20in%20the%20UT%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Rajouri%20Poonch%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operations%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Operation%20Sarpvinash%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20in%202003%20to%20eliminate%20terrorists%20from%20the%20same%20areas%20in%20the%20South%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmy%20Chief%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%20recently%20stated%20that%20terrorist%20activities%20had%20almost%20vanished%20in%20the%20area%20since%202003%2C%20but%20the%20western%20adversary%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20revive%20it%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20along%20with%20the%20Northern%20Command%20had%20also%20held%20detailed%20discussions%20with%20the%20Corps%20Commanders%20on%20ways%20to%20tackle%20the%20threat%20from%20these%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operations%20are%20being%20launched%20in%20close%20monitoring%20by%20the%20Army%20Headquarters%20and%20the%20Northern%20Army%20Command%20in%20Udhampur%20and%20were%20planned%20soon%20after%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20held%20a%20security%20meeting%20with%20all%20stakeholders%20including%20the%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20Army%2C%20intelligence%20agencies%20including%20both%20internal%20and%20external%20ones%2C%20police%20officials%20from%20both%20state%20and%20central%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorthern%20Army%20Commander%20Lt%20Gen%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20has%20held%20coordination%20meetings%20with%20the%20top%20security%20forces%20brass%20in%20both%20the%20Jammu%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20regions%20for%20coordinated%20action%20against%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%20has%20also%20started%20the%20process%20of%20inducting%20more%20troops%20in%20the%20Rajouri-Poonch%20sector.%20The%20troops'%20induction%20process%20has%20also%20started%2C%20along%20with%20the%20strengthening%20of%20the%20intelligence%20setup%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20forces%20are%20also%20confident%20about%20the%20local%20support%20to%20thwart%20terrorism%20in%20the%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20despite%20provocation%20by%20terrorists%20to%20attack%20an%20Army%20vehicle%20in%20the%20Krisna%20Ghati%20area%2C%20the%20troops%20did%20not%20fire%20back%20as%20a%20lot%20of%20civilians%20were%20present%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swift%20action%20initiated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%20against%20own%20officers%20and%20men%20in%20the%20death%20of%20civilians%20post%20December%2021%20encounter%20has%20also%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705158540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fn17re86g_indian-army-generic_625x300_08_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-launches-new-operation-sarvashakti-to-thwart-paks-plan-to-revive-terrorism-in-j-k-4856726%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20major%20step%20towards%20thwarting%20Pakistan's%20attempts%20to%20increase%20terrorist%20activities%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20is%20launching%20Operation%20Sarvashakti.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-launches-new-operation-sarvashakti-to-thwart-paks-plan-to-revive-terrorism-in-j-k-4856726%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-launches-new-operation-sarvashakti-to-thwart-paks-plan-to-revive-terrorism-in-j-k-4856726%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-launches-new-operation-sarvashakti-to-thwart-paks-plan-to-revive-terrorism-in-j-k-4856726%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cockpit%20window%20crack%20forces%20ANA%20Boeing%20flight%20in%20Japan%20to%20turn%20back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705