%20however%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20is%20holding%20discussions%20with%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20listening%20to%20my%20supporters...Haven't%20taken%20a%20decision%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Mumbai%20South%20MP%20said%20when%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20chalking%20out%20a%20plan%20with%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20rumours%2C%20he%20said%20while%20responding%20to%20a%20query%20on%20reports%20in%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20media%20that%20he%20was%20quitting%20the%20Congress%20to%20join%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20group%20had%20staked%20a%20claim%20to%20contest%20the%20Mumbai%20South%20constituency%2C%20represented%20by%20Mr%20Deora%20before%202014%2C%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%2C%20which%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20the%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20statement%20issued%20last%20Sunday%2C%20Mr%20Deora%20said%20that%20if%20such%20statements%20by%20an%20%26quot%3Balliance%20partner%26quot%3B%20don't%20stop%2C%20his%20party%20too%20can%20announce%20candidates%20for%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20is%20an%20alliance%20partner%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar%20faction)%20in%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Deora%20had%20said%20since%20the%20formal%20talks%20on%20sharing%20of%20seats%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20concluded%2C%20nobody%20should%20make%20claims%20and%20counter-claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Deora%2C%20son%20of%20Congress%20veteran%20Murli%20Deora%2C%20had%20won%20the%20Mumbai%20South%20seat%20in%202004%20and%202009.%20He%20ended%20up%20as%20the%20first%20runner-up%20in%20the%20subsequent%20elections%20in%202014%20and%202019%20against%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Undivided)%20leader%20Arvind%20Sawant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Deora%20had%20said%20his%20family%20represented%20the%20seat%20for%2050%20yea