m%20Dube%20and%20a%20cameo%20by%20Jitesh%20Sharma%20helped%20India%20secure%20a%20six-wicket%20win%20over%20Afghanistan%20in%20the%20first%20T20I%20of%20the%20three-match%20series%20at%20Mohali%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20YouTube%20channel%20after%20the%20match%2C%20Aakash%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20Rohit%20(Sharma)%20and%20Shubman%20(Gill)%20got%20out%2C%20Tilak%20Varma%20was%20there%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20was%20sent%20up%20the%20order.%20Tilak%20Varma%20played%20well%20for%20some%20time%20but%20then%20also%20got%20out%20off%20(Azmatullah)%20Omarzai's%20bowling.%20Tilak%20Varma%20has%20not%20grabbed%20his%20chance%20fully.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20Tilak%20Varma%20play%20the%20next%20match%3F%20I%20feel%20he%20might%20get%20dropped%20because%20if%20both%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20become%20available%2C%20who%20will%20go%20out%3F%20No%20one%20can%20leave%20Shivam%20Dube%20out%20nor%20will%20anyone%20touch%20Rinku%20Singh.%20Do%20not%20know%20about%20Shubman%20Gill%20but%20I%20feel%20Tilak%20Varma%20might%20be%20dropped%20for%20the%20next%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2016%20T20Is%20so%20far%2C%20Tilak%20has%20scored%20336%20runs%20in%2015%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2033.60%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20139.41%2C%20with%20two%20half-centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20following%20a%20great%20debut%20series%20in%20West%20Indies%2C%20Tilak's%20performances%20have%20not%20been%20at%20his%20very%20best%20as%20he%20has%20scored%20just%20163%20runs%20in%2010%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2023.28%2C%20with%20one%20fifty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20Chopra%20was%20also%20critical%20of%20wicketkeeper-batter%20Jitesh%20Sharma's%20dismissal%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20convert%20his%20fine%20starts%20to%20solidify%20his%20spot%20in%20the%20team%2C%20with%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Sanju%20Samson%20also%20battling%20for%20his%20spot%20as%20glovesmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20Jitesh%20played%20a%20good%20knock.%20Let%20me%20put%20my%20hand%20up%20and%20say%20that%20Jitesh%20played%20well%20but%20he%20will%20have%20to%20be%20mindful%20that%20he%20needs%20to%20finish%20matches%20because%20he%20could%20have%20done%20that.%20He%20is%20batting%20so%20beautifully.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20converts%20his%2031%20runs%20to%2045-50%20and%20finishes%20the%20match%2C%20there%20would%20not%20be%20any%20doubt%2C%20because%20his%20place%20is%20not%20yet%20cemented.%20It%20is%20going%20to%20take%20some%20time%20because%2C%20for%20that%20slot%2C%20Sanju%20Samson%20is%20there%20for%20sure%2C%20don't%20rule%20out%20KL%20Rahul%20as%20you%20might%20see%20him%20bat%20down%20the%20order%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20and%20Rishabh%20Pant's%20name%20can%20come%20if%20he%20gets%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20put%20to%20bat%20first%20by%20India%2C%20Afghanistan%20had%20a%20good%20start%2C%20with%20skipper%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%20(25%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Rahmanullah%20Gurbaz%20(23%20in%2028%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20adding%2050%20runs%20for%20the%20first%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Indian%20bowlers%20reduced%20Afghanistan%20to%2057%2F3%2C%20A%2068-run%20partnership%20between%20Azmatullah%20Omarzai%20(29%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Mohammed%20Nabi%20(42%20in%2027%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20bringing%20them%20back%20into%20the%20match.%20A%20solid%20partnership%20between%20Najibullah%20Zadran%20(19*)%20and%20Karim%20Janat%20(9*)%20at%20the%20back%20end%20of%20the%20innings%20took%20them%20to%20158%2F5%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxar%20Patel%20(2%2F23)%20and%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20(2%2F33)%20were%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20India.%20Shivam%20Dube%20got%20one%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chase%20of%20159%2C%20India%20lost%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20for%20a%20duck%20on%20his%20return%20to%20T20Is.%20Shubman%20Gill%20(23%20in%2012%20balls%2C%20five%20fours)%20showed%20intent%20but%20could%20not%20convert%20his%20start%20into%20a%20big%20score.%20A%2044-run%20stand%20between%20Shivam%20Dube%20and%20Tilak%20Varma%20(26%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20brought%20India%20back%20into%20the%20match.%20Later%2C%20a%2045-run%20stand%20between%20Shivam%20and%20Jitesh%20Sharma%20(31%20in%2020%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours)%20took%20India%20close%20to%20a%20win.%20Dube%20scored%20his%20second%20T20I%20half-century%2C%20getting%2060%20in%2040%20balls%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes%20and%20joined%20forces%20with%20Rinku%20Singh%20(16*)%20to%20win%20the%20game%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMujeeb%20ur%20Rahman%20took%20two%20wickets%20for%20Afghanistan%2C%20while%20Omarzai%20got%20a%20wicket.%20Dube%20got%20a%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award%20for%20his%20all-round%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705157220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fnu00mbmg_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhasnt-grabbed-his-chance-ex-india-star-names-player-to-be-dropped-for-virat-kohli-in-2nd-t20i-4847866%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20wasn't%20part%20of%20India's%20team%20for%20the%201st%20T20I%20vs%20Afghanistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ayodhya%20Dazzles%20As%20Thousands%20Of%20Diyas%20Lit%20Around%20Images%20Of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20grand%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20R