%20placed%20those%20pictures%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20there%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20society%20will%20remain%20healthy%20only%20when%20all%20its%20sections%20remain%20united...%20Those%20who%20want%20to%20divide%20the%20society%2C%20want%20to%20spread%20poison%20for%20immediate%20political%20gains%20are%20not%20only%20enemies%20of%20the%20society%20but%20also%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20need%20to%20teach%20a%20lesson%20to%20such%20elements%20because%20they%20are%20our%20own.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20to%20make%20them%20aware...%20they%20need%20to%20be%20brought%20on%20the%20right%20path.%20This%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20not%20institutionally%20but%20in%20our%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20Vice%20President%20expressed%20confidence%20that%2C%20under%20the%20new%20leadership%2C%20Rajasthan%20would%20progress%20at%20a%20fast%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20national%20interest%20should%20always%20be%20paramount%20and%20warned%20people%20against%20those%20who%20sow%20seeds%20of%20division%20and%20disharmony%20in%20the%20society%2C%20undermine%20the%20country's%20achievements%2C%20and%20spread%20misconceptions%20about%20its%20progress%20for%20immediate%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Premchand%20Bairwa%20were%20present%20at%20the%20event.%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20also%20visited%20the%20house%20of%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Harishankar%20Bhabhada%20to%20inquire%20about%20his%20well-being.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705154880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Feiluiti8_vice-president-jag