%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Delhi%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20Amritsar%2C%20and%20Ludhiana%2C%20the%20maximum%20temperatures%C2%A0%20were%2013.4%C2%B0%20Celsius%2C%2010.5%C2%B0%20Celsius%2C%209.5%C2%B0%20Celsius%20and%2010.6%C2%B0%20Celsius%2C%E2%80%9D%20Faizan%20Arif%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20weather%20channel%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChilai%20Kalan%2C%20the%2040-day%20winter%20period%20which%20starts%20in%20Kashmir%20on%20December%2021%2C%20is%20marked%20by%20incessant%20snowfall%20and%20subzero%20temperature%20that%20causes%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20residents%20who%20often%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20the%20sight%20of%20frozen%20drinking%20water%20taps%20and%20no%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20Rashid%2C%20a%20faculty%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Geoinformatics%2C%20University%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Valley%20is%20witnessing%20snowless%20winter%20after%20seven%20years%2C%20which%20will%20have%20a%20cascading%20effect%20on%20the%20generation%20capacity%20of%20hydropower%20projects%2C%20agriculture%20activities%20and%20winter%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashid%20warned%20that%20in%20case%20the%20dry%20spell%20continued%2C%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20%E2%80%9Chigher%20mass%20loss%20of%20glaciers%E2%80%9D%20which%20will%20not%20only%20impact%20the%20flow%20of%20water%20in%20the%20streams%20and%20rivers%20of%20Kashmir%20during%20the%20summers%20but%20also%20have%20long-term%20effect%20on%20the%20Himalayan%20ecosystems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJhelum%20river%2C%20the%20major%20source%20of%20irrigation%20in%20Kashmir%20which%20bisects%20the%20Srinagar%20city%2C%20ran%20at%20historic%20low%20level%20in%20September%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13090739%2FIMG_3744.jp