ists.%20Due%20to%20lack%20of%20snow%2C%20winter%20sports%20activities%20such%20as%20snowboarding%20and%20skiing%20at%20the%20hill%20resort%20have%20taken%20a%20backseat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20best%20of%20news%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Brian%20Newman%2C%20who%20works%20with%20Gulmarg%20Ski%20Patrol%20and%20Avalanche%20Centre%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20average%2C%20there%20is%2050-70%20cm%20of%20snow%20at%204000%20metres%20which%20fell%20on%20December%2010.%20Without%20any%20new%20snow%2C%20we%20have%20insufficient%20snowpack%20to%20open%20the%20ski%20area%20as%20yet.%20The%20bad%20news%20is%20that%20there%20is%20no%20forecast%20of%20snow%20for%20next%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1470160X21003551%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScience%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EDirect%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20the%20average%20annual%20mean%20maximum%20temperature%20in%20Kashmir%20increased%20by%20two%20notches%20between%201980%20to%202020%2C%20an%20increase%20of%200.5%C2%B0%20Celsius%20per%20decade%20which%20is%20far%20more%20than%200.2%20degree%20Celsius%20increase%20recorded%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarhat%20Naik%2C%20a%20national-level%20snowboarder%20from%20Tangmarg%20area%20of%20north%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20that%20the%20bowl%20of%20Gulmarg%20is%20witnessing%20an%20unprecedented%20flower%20bloom%20which%20usually%20happened%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20spring%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20shocking%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naik%2C%20who%20also%20coordinates%20the%20National%20Winter%20Games%20which%20are%20held%20in%20Gulmarg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaik%2C%20a%20snowboarding%20instructor%2C%20said%20that%20the%20deficit%20in%20snowfall%20has%20adversely%20impacted%20the%20winter%20tourism%20economy%20of%20Gulmarg.%20The%20fate%20of%20the%20National%20Winter%20Games%2C%20which%20are%20held%20in%20Gulmarg%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20February%2C%20also%20hangs%20in%20the%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20lack%20of%20snowfall%20has%20also%20affected%20the%20preparations%20of%20sportspersons%20like%20skiers%20and%20snowboarders%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20hit%20the%20slopes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dry%20spell%20has%20also%20led%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%20hotel%20bookings%2C%20especially%20in%20Gulmarg%20which%20used%20to%20be%20thronged%20by%20tourists%20in%20winter.%20Mohammad%20Shafi%2C%20an%20official%20with%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20said%20that%20the%20occupancy%20of%20hotels%20in%20Gulmarg%20has%20shrunk%20by%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13090709%2FIMG_3753.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13090709%2FIMG_3753.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13090709%2FIMG_3753-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692770%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESpring%20flowers%20blooming%20on%20the%20meadows%20of%20Gulmarg%20due%20to%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%20prevailing%20in%20Kashmir.%20Photo%3A%20By%20special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTourists%20are%20not%20coming%20to%20Kashmir%20these%20days.%20There%20have%20been%20hundreds%20of%20cancellations%20of%20hotel%20bookings%20as%20there%20has%20been%20no%20snowfall%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mushtaq%20Chaya%2C%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20hoteliers%20from%20Kashmir%20whose%20properties%20are%20located%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzoor%20Ahmad%20Pakhtoon%2C%20President%20of%20Kashmir%20Houseboat%20Association%20said%20that%20the%20tourism%20industry%20has%20suffered%20badly%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20precipitation%20this%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHouseboats%20are%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20the%20itinerary%20of%20tourists%20visiting%20the%20Valley%20but%20these%20days%20many%20of%20them%20are%20stranded%20on%20mud%20cakes%20along%20the%20parched%20banks%20of%20Jehlum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20bookings%20are%20getting%20cancelled.%20While%20the%20houseboats%20registered%2060-70%20percent%20occupancy%20last%20year%2C%20it%20has%20fallen%20to%2020-25%20percent%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pakhtoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20prayer%20called%20%E2%80%98Salatul%20Istisqa%E2%80%99%20was%20offered%20at%20Jamia%20Masjid%20in%20Srinagar%20on%20Friday%20to%20seek%20divine%20intervention%20in%20ending%20the%20prevailing%20dry%20weather%20conditions%20in%20Kashmir.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20devotees%20participated%20in%20the%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deficit%20in%20precipitation%20has%20also%20shadowed%20the%20generation%20capacity%20of%20hydroelectricity%20projects%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%20which%20is%20reeling%20under%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20power%20crises%20in%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20subzero%20temperatures%2C%20the%20water%20flow%20from%20the%20glaciers%20and%20alpine%20lakes%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20has%20decreased%20significantly%2C%20which%20has%20reduced%20generation%20by%20around%2070%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20high%20demand%20of%20electricity%20in%20winters%2C%20the%20situation%20will%20worsen%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20precipitation%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20coming%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20official%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Power%20Development%20Corporation%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%