e%20PM%20and%20that%20it%20was%20purely%20a%20military%20decision.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Jo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20is%20appropriate).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20handed%20a%20hot%20potato.%20With%20this%20carte%20blanche%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20now%20totally%20on%20me.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20sat%20silently%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20All%20was%20quiet%20save%20for%20the%20ticking%20of%20the%20wall%20clock.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20author%2C%20General%20Naravane%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20final%20release%20date%20for%20the%20book%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20we%20should%20%E2%80%9Ccheck%20with%20publishers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20carefully%20review%20all%20our%20books%20to%20ensure%20quality%20content%20and%20this%20process%20may%20impact%20publishing%20timelines%20based%20on%20the%20necessary%20work%20involved.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20editorial%20process%2C%20we%20are%20scheduled%20to%20publish%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20book%20in%202024%20and%20we%20are%20working%20towards%20meeting%20that%20timeline%2C%E2%80%9D%20Milee%20Ashwarya%2C%20publisher%2C%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20India%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Naravane%20retired%20as%20the%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20on%20April%2030%2C%202022%20and%20has%20since%20completed%20his%20PhD%20in%20defence%20and%20strategic%20studies%20from%20Punjabi%20University%2C%20Patiala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApril%2030%2C%20or%20May%20would%20be%20a%20time%20of%20considerable%20ferment%20in%20the%20country%2C%20when%20the%20news%20cycle%20would%20be%20fully%20consumed%20by%20the%20elections%20expected%20at%20the%20time%2C%20most%20of%20the%20contours%20of%20the%20political%20campaign%20would%20be%20almost%20set%20by%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1