https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338238%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShanker%20officially%20launched%20his%20company%20which%20he%20runs%20along%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Kanchan%20Meena.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20farmers%20take%20a%20shortcut%20and%20keep%20multiplying%20spawns%20using%20the%20commercial%20spawns%2C%20instead%20of%20preparing%20a%20different%20tissue%20culture%20and%20mother%20spawn.%20This%20reduces%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20spawns%20and%20makes%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20diseases.%20While%20they%20may%20not%20observe%20the%20effect%20immediately%2C%20it%20is%20observed%20by%20farmers%20only%20when%20they%20get%20a%20low%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Shanker%20earns%20a%20decent%20profit%20today%2C%20it%20is%20not%20all%20roses%20all%20the%20time.%20%E2%80%9CAlong%20with%20profits%2C%20we%20also%20incur%20losses%20sometimes.%20Last%20year%2C%20we%20faced%20losses%20worth%20Rs%2027%20lakh.%20I%20was%20receiving%20complaints%20of%20low%20yield.%20When%20I%20checked%20the%20machinery%2C%20I%20found%20out%20there%20was%20a%20thin%20hair%20size%20leakage%20that%20contaminated%20the%20spawns%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20I%20get%20discouraged%20by%20such%20situations%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20quitting.%20But%20then%20I%20look%20back%20at%20my%20journey%20and%20I%20feel%20overwhelmed%20to%20have%20come%20so%20far.%20I%20