.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D338189%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Embark%20on%20a%20winter%20wildlife%20expedition%20across%20India's%20national%20parks%2C%20encountering%20the%20majestic%20Bengal%20tigers%20in%20Jim%20Corbett%20and%20the%20migratory%20birds%20of%20Keoladeo.%20Here's%20a%20winter%20safari%20guide%20to%20help%20you%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338189%2Fbest-national-park-wildlife-safaris-in-winter-adventure-travel-guide-vacation%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22If%20Congress%20is%20%E2%80%98Anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%2C%20Are%20Shankaracharyas%20Also%20%E2%80%98Anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%3F%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12193806%2Fimage-1732.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ever%20since%20the%20Congress%20has%20declined%20its%20invitation%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%2C%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20left%20no%20opportunity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fbjp-calls-congress-anti-hindu-for-declining-ram-temple-consecration-invite-2843222%5C%22%3Edeclare%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98anti-Ram%E2%80%99.%20The%20Congress%20has%20categorically%20termed%20the%20ceremony%20as%20one%20that%20is%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbreaking-congress-declines-invitation-to-ram-temple-inauguration-calls-its-clearly-an-rss-bjp-event%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%2FRSS%20event%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20said%20that%20religion%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98personal%20matter%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20has%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20a%20political%20project%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20response%20is%20consistent%20with%20its%20opposition%20to%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20by%20Hindutva%20forces.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20being%20built%20atop%20the%20dome%20of%20the%20mosque%20is%20reason%20enough%20for%20all%20democratic-minded%20citizens%20who%20believe%20that%20Hindutva%20politics%2C%20since%20the%201990s%2C%20has%20expanded%20itself%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20the%20grave%20injustice%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%20to%20reach%20where%20it%20is%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20is%20not%20merely%20any%20temple.%20It%20is%20a%20temple%20where%20once%20a%20mosque%20stood%20and%20was%20brought%20down%20with%20sheer%20force%20of%20hate%20and%20muscle.%20It%20was%20an%20episode%20of%20national%20shame%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20which%20is%20being%20carried%20by%20the%20secular%20parties%20even%20today.%20The%20BJP%20has%20choreographed%20so%20much%20hype%20and%20hoopla%20to%20strip%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20of%20its%20history.%20It%20sees%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20as%20epochal%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20history%2C%20but%20wants%20everyone%20to%20conveniently%20forget%20about%20the%20violence%20that%20eventually%20led%20to%20its%20creation.%20For%20this%20precise%20reason%2C%20it%20has%20done%20everything%20on%20its%20part%20to%20wipe%20out%20any%20memory%20of%20its%20own%20violent%20history%20and%20the%20role%20that%20it%20played%20in%20sharply%20polarising%20India%20along%20religious%20lines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20would%20have%20wished%20that%20the%20opposition%20parties%20would%20have%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20is%20not%20one%20based%20on%20faith%20but%20is%20a%20mere%20instrument%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20perpetuate%20a%20majoritarian%20common%20sense.%20Barring%20the%20Left%20parties%2C%20none%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20taken%20such%20a%20stance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20non-attendance%20has%20given%20secular-minded%20citizens%20something%20to%20hold%20on%20to.%20More%20than%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas%2C%20the%20foremost%20flag%20bearers%20of%20the%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20to%20give%20the%20event%20a%20miss%2C%20has%20certainly%20exposed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20scheme%20to%20play%20around%20with%20people%E2%80%99s%20faith.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%204%20Highest%20Gurus%20of%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Participate%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Pran%20Pratistha%2C%E2%80%99%20Explains%20Pro-Hindutva%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20amplified%20the%20boycott%20by%20the%20Shankaracharyas%2C%20and%20questioned%20the%20BJP%20on%20why%20it%20is%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20perform%20a%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20an%20incomplete%20temple.%20The%20Shankaracharyas%20believe%20that%20the%20Hindu%20Shastras%20do%20not%20permit%20anyone%20to%20perform%20consecration%20of%20a%20deity%20in%20an%20incomplete%20temple.%20They%20also%20believe%20that%20January%2022%20falls%20in%20the%20lunar%20month%20of%20Paus%2C%20which%20is%20inauspicious%20for%20the%20ceremony%2C%20while%20also%20claiming%20that%20the%20ceremony%20is%20being%20conducted%20in%20haste%20to%20hand%20political%20and%20electoral%20gains%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Are%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20also%20%E2%80%9Canti-Hindu%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-Ram%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20BJP%20should%20answer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20using%20the%20ceremony%20for%20political%20gains%2C%20and%20precisely%20that%20is%20what%20the%20saffron%20party%20wants%20people%20to%20ignore%20by%20manufacturing%20a%20mass%20hysteria%20around%20the%20ceremony.%20A%20pliant%20media%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20has%20only%20aided%20and%20abetted%20the%20goal%20for%20the%20BJP.%20It%20has%20failed%20to%20question%20the%20BJP%2C%20even%20minutely%2C%20on%20how%20the%20political%20celebration%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20its%20ministers%20of%20the%20ceremony%20is%20not%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20promises%20a%20clear%20separation%20of%20religion%20and%20the%20State.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20ceremony%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20presiding%20over%20it%20himself%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20instance%20of%20how%20the%20BJP%20has%20successfully%20merged%20religious%20matters%20with%20State%20policy.%20With%20the%20blatant%20campaigning%20around%20welcoming%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20the%20temple%20by%20all%20the%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20from%20top%20to%20bottom%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20simultaneous%20announcement%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fayodhya-pm-narendra-modi-ayodhya-railway-station-airport-inauguration-ayodhya-dham-2482149-2023-12-30%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20worth%20Rs%2031%2C000%20crore%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20new%20airport%20and%20railway%20facility%20in%20the%20town%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20doubt%20about%20how%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20milk%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20divisive%20politics%20to%20dive%20India%20even%20further.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20all%20the%20canvassing%20by%20the%20BJP%20against%20the%20Congress%20for%20allegedly%20being%20%E2%80%9Canti-Hindu%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20decided%20to%20not%20visit%20Ayodhya%20(for%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPran%20Pratishtha%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Ram%20Temple).%20But%20there%20is%20no%20outrage%20over%20this.%20Does%20this%20not%20hurt%20religion%3F%20It%20is%20absolutely%20wrong%20to%20do%20politics%20over%20religious%20rituals.%20We%20are%20not%20declining%20a%20visit%20(to%20Ayodhya).%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20the%20January%2022%20event%20in%20Ayodhya%20that%20is%20being%20held%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20the%20RSS%20chief.%20Shankaracharyas%20are%20not%20going%20to%20that%20event%20either.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20disgusting%20politics%20that%20is%20being%20done%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20event%20is%20religious%2C%20then%20is%20it%20happening%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20of%20the%20four%20Peeths%3F%20All%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20said%20clearly%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPran%20Pratishtha%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20an%20incomplete%20temple%20cannot%20be%20done.%20If%20this%20event%20is%20not%20religious%2C%20then%20it%20is%20political%E2%80%A6%20It%20is%20not%20acceptable%20that%20the%20people%20of%20a%20political%20party%20are%20sitting%20as%20middlemen%20between%20me%20and%20my%20God%E2%80%A6%20A%20political%20group%20is%20acting%20like%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ethekedar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%A6%20Which%20%E2%80%98Panchang%E2%80%99%20has%20the%20BJP%20referred%20to%20before%20finalising%20the%20date%3F%20The%20date%20has%20been%20chosen%20keeping%20the%20elections%20in%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20even%20before%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20the%20ceremony%20was%20being%20planned%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20project%2C%20wherein%20the%20attempted%20appropriation%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20to%20advance%20its%20Hindu%20supremacist%20politics%20was%20writ%20large.%20Contrary%20to%20what%20the%20opposition%20parties%20may%20think%2C%20common%20people%20who%20are%20not%20affiliated%20to%20any%20political%20party%20are%20wise%20enough%20to%20see%20the%20blatant%20politicking%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-the-bjp-the-hindu-card-is-no-longer-as-potent-as-it-once-was%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Card%20Is%20No%20Longer%20as%20Potent%20as%20It%20Once%20Was%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20certain%20sections%20in%20the%20Congress%20which%20are%20not%20convinced%20about%20the%20Congress%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20boycott%20the%20event.%20They%20believe%20that%20they%20may%20have%20a%20tough%20time%20explaining%20the%20party%20logic%20to%20people%20while%20canvassing.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20also%20questioned%20the%20party%20leadership%20on%20the%20decision%20and%20have%20requested%20it%20to%20reconsider.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20perhaps%20the%20time%20when%20the%20leadership%20could%20also%20rein%20in%20and%20reorient%20the%20Congress%20towards%20taking%20ethical%20positions%20which%20are%20consistent%20with%20its%20party%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegional%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20and%20many%20others%2C%20including%20the%20right-wing%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20group%20had%20already%20called%20out%20the%20political%20instrumentalisation%20of%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony.%20The%20Congress%20has%20come%20in%20late%20but%20now%20should%20stick%20to%20it%20with%20aggression.%20This%20is%20the%20time%20for%20the%20party%20to%20forcefully%20represent%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20original%20liberal-democratic%20idea%20of%20India.%20Only%20then%2C%20it%20can%20retain%20its%20relevance%20in%20the%20times%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20onslaught%2C%20and%20not%20by%20capitulating%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20a%20manufactured%20mass%20hysteria.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705069802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12193806%2Fimage-1732.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fif-congress-is-anti-hindu-are-shankaracharyas-also-anti-hindu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20grand%20inauguration%20ceremony%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20presiding%20over%20it%20himself%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20instance%20of%20how%20the%20BJP%20has%20succeeded%20in%20merging%20religious%20matters%20with%20State%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fif-congress-is-anti-hindu-are-shankaracharyas-also-anti-hindu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Candidate%20who%20champions%20autonomy%20from%20China%20wins%20Taiwan%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705069140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-lai-ching-te-taiwan_6420278.jpg%3F20240113142031%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftaiwan-election-candidate-who-champions-autonomy-from-china-takes-early-lead-13046870%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20winner%20of%20Taiwan's%20presidential%20election%20has%20said%20voters%20have%20shown%20the%20world%20%26quot%3Bhow%20much%20we%20cherish%20democracy%26quot%3B%20after%20his%20party%2C%20which%20champions%20autonomy%20from%20China%2C%20secured%20a%20third%20term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A215%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftaiwan-election-candidate-who-champions-autonomy-from-china-takes-early-lead-13046870%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftaiwan-election-candidate-who-champions-autonomy-from-china-takes-early-lead-13046870%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftaiwan-election-candidate-who-champions-autonomy-from-china-takes-early-lead-13046870%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Represents%20the%20Sanatan%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Seer%20of%20Puri%20or%20Shri%20Modi%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11120348%2FPrime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_performing_Bhoomi_Pujan_at_%25E2%2580%2598Shree_Ram_Janmabhoomi_Mandir%25E2%2580%2599_in_Ayodhya_Uttar_Pradesh_on_August_05_2020.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPredictably%2C%20the%20Sangh%2C%20now%20busy%20at%20the%20temple%20site%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20has%20begun%20lambasting%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20for%20its%20refusal%20to%20attend%20the%20so-called%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20grave%20irony%20that%20attends%20this%20political%20configuration%20is%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20made%20precisely%20the%20same%20critique%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20ceremony%20as%20has%20been%20made%20by%20the%20venerated%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20and%20the%20other%20three%20shankaracharyas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20highly%20regarded%20seer%20has%20remarked%20that%20any%20consecration%20ceremony%20must%20follow%20due%20theological%20processes%2F%20rituals%2C%20as%20laid%20out%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESkand%20Purana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFailing%20such%20due%20observances%20authorised%20and%20executed%20by%20enshrined%20religious%20heads%2C%20the%20seer%20has%20cautioned%20that%20the%20idol%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20undesirable%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%2C%20mocking%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20gestures%20that%20habitually%20accompany%20his%20victory%20public%20addresses%2C%20asked%20whether%20he%20(the%20seer)%20is%20expected%20to%20sit%20and%20clap%20while%20Modi%20fronts%20the%20consecration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seer%20has%20underscored%20the%20unflattering%20point%20that%20the%20event%20is%20merely%20a%20public%20relations%20show%20aimed%20at%20lifting%20the%20electoral%20prospects%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20question%20must%20be%20asked%3A%20who%20is%20more%20proximate%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESanata%20Dharma%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20seer%20of%20Puri%20or%20the%20executive%20head%20of%20the%20constitutional%20republic%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%204%20Highest%20Gurus%20of%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Participate%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Pranpratistha%2C%E2%80%99%20Explains%20Pro-Hindutva%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20if%20the%20Congress%20is%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20wrong%20for%20not%20attending%20the%20ceremony%20scheduled%20for%20January%2022%2C%20why%20not%20also%20the%20Shakaracharya%20of%20Puri%2C%20who%20has%20also%20declined%20to%20be%20present%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlternately%2C%20why%20is%20the%20Sangh%20fighting%20shy%20of%20engaging%20the%20Shankaracharya%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShastrartha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20or%20scholarly%20debate%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20hallowed%20traditions%20of%20the%20Sanatan%2C%20so%20that%20lay%20Hindus%20might%20better%20understand%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20issue%20at%20hand%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20now%2C%20it%20does%20seem%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20closer%20to%20the%20Sanatan%20position%20than%20those%20who%20are%20so%20relentlessly%20propagating%20the%20Sanatan%20character%20of%20the%20event%20to%20come.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20would%20it%20not%20be%20apposite%20for%20media%20houses%20to%20foreground%20the%20historic%20nature%20of%20the%20schism%20here%20between%20the%20Shankaracharya%20and%20the%20forces%20of%20political%20Hinduism%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20which%20side%20may%20the%20nationalist%20corporates%20be%20on%20who%20now%20elbow%20the%20said%20media%20channels%20in%20establishment%20directions%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20does%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20case%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20little%20reason%20to%20cower%2C%20given%20that%20its%20reservations%20have%20been%20so%20openly%20and%20authoritatively%20endorsed%20by%20the%20highest%20religious%20supremo%20among%20the%20Sanatan%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20messaging%20wherewithal%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20the%20resources%20to%20match%20the%20onslaught%20of%20the%20official%20armoury.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20thereby%20hangs%20an%20unlovely%20tale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705066793000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in