ys%2C%20%E2%80%9CTier%20two%20cities%2C%20known%20for%20their%20price%20sensitivity%20in%20comparison%20to%20tier%20one%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20have%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20promising%20market%20for%20us.%20Despite%20the%20price%20sensitivity%2C%20our%20outlets%20in%20tier-two%20cities%20have%20demonstrated%20significant%20success.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20or%20within%20the%20next%20year%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20further%20expand%20our%20presence%20in%20the%20existing%20cities%20and%20explore%20additional%20tier-two%20cities%20in%20proximity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20they%20have%20collaborated%20with%20another%20food%20business%20to%20open%2013%20outlets%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704809260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D337833%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Realising%20that%20there%20were%20no%20good%20momo%20joints%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Zomoz%20founder%20Shouvik%20Dhar%20innovated%20an%20automated%20momo%20machine%20that%20can%20make%20lakhs%20of%20momos%20in%20a%20day!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337833%2Fzomoz-startup-nit-engineer-innovated-automated-momo-machine-earns-crores%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Child%20Labourer%20Rescued%20By%20Kailash%20Satyarthi%2C%20He%E2%80%99s%20Now%20a%20Lawyer%20Fighting%20For%20Rights%20of%20Hundreds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESix-year-old%20Amar%20Lal%20from%20Rajasthan%20was%20never%20concerned%20with%20what%20year%2C%20month%2C%20week%20or%20day%20it%20was.%20His%20routine%20was%20the%20same.%20Every%20morning%20the%20family%20%E2%80%94%20hailing%20from%20the%20Banjara%20nomadic%20tribe%20in%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20would%20pack%20their%20meagre%20belongings%